Hisense’s Hi-Season Summer campaign is now on, and you stand a chance to win a new Hisense fridge. All you need to do to enter the competition is make an online purchase of any product that is part of the Hisense Hi-Season promotion from Takealot, Makro, HiFi Corp, Hirsch’s Homestore, Game, Everyshop, FNB Connect or New World. One you have done this, email your proof of purchase to prize@hisense.co.za to stand a chance of winning. The fridge up for grabs is the awesome Hisense H230BTSA, which boasts a premium appearance with a frameless door and an integrated U-shaped cabinet that will suit any kitchen aesthetic. This great style is coupled with an easy-to-clean design to ensure your fridge remains in top condition, as well as having a metal back for increased safety and protection. The Hisense H230BTSA also features an A+ energy rating, which saves you money and reduces its environmental impact. With its 165-litre net capacity, split into a 122-litre fridge and a 43-litre freezer, makes it easy to store all your food. On the inside, it is illuminated by LEDs that floods your fridge with light so you will never struggle to find anything. Hisense’s Hi-Season online promotion is running from 21 March to 15 April 2022, so don’t miss out — and don’t forget to submit your proof of purchase to prize@hisense.co.za to stand a chance of winning your own Hisense Combi Refrigerator. Winners will be announced on social media: Click here to find out more about the Hisense Hi-Season Summer promotion.